The revival of reality
Little <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ho - ho</ENAMEX> 's line - " Do n't beat me any more ! " - reflects one of the more common themes of TV shows done in <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> .
