" <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> serials depict the daily life of ordinary people the way they do because of their development process , " says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ko Yu - fen</ENAMEX> , an associate professor of mass communications at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Shih Hsin University</ENAMEX> , who has done a study of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> TV drama .
