The hard - pressed daughter in law
The story of <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">The Astonishing Daughter - in - Law</ENAMEX> is quite simple .
The daughter - in - law , played by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chang Yu - yen</ENAMEX> , is mistreated by her mother - in - law , and , with outsiders butting in and causing trouble , she gets abused from beginning to end .
